00:00:31.980 --> 00:00:35.100
Walk up to your enemy and push the CQC button 3 times.

00:00:35.280 --> 00:00:37.280
Snake will do 2 punches and 1 kick.

00:00:37.380 --> 00:00:39.800
After the kick, the enemy is going to go fall on the ground.

00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:44.480
Depending on what difficulty you're on, it's going to take 1 or 2 combos to knock out your enemy.

00:00:44.720 --> 00:00:47.720
